<D>__{can you stop him, please?}
<L>__{interior union county court house, courtroom later.}
<A>__{it's a very drab, no frills courtroom. judge lee is seated on the bench looking over some documents. mike is sitting next leo. seated at the next table is stu thatcher, attorney for the office of public guardian. mike is tapping his pen.}
<C>__{judge lee}
<D>__{any word from his daughter? mr. flaherty?}
