<D>__{who?}
<C>__{mike}
<D>__{your daughter.}
<C>__{leo}
<D>__{she's late? she's probably at the store buying some crap or something.}
<C>__{mike}
<D>__{ok.}
<A>__{mike turns back to the judge and shrugs.}
<C>__{judge lee}
<D>__{ok, then as, mr. poplar has been deemed incapacitated by this court, i'm appointing the office of public guardian to serve as the guardian for his person and property. do you have the order for me to sign, mr. thatcher?}
<C>__{thatcher}
<D>__{yes, i do, your honor.}
<C>__{judge lee}
<D>__{then please approach.}
