<D>__{yeah.}
<C>__{thatcher}
<D>__{how long have you known him? two weeks?}
<A>__{mike is suddenly put on the spot.}
<C>__{mike}
<D>__{more like five.}
<C>__{thatcher}
<D>__{really? and now you want to be his guardian?}
